        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "These are the things wherein Solomon was instructed — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "By David his father, and by the Spirit of God. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "After the first measure threescore cubits — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "According to the measure which was first fixed. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "The porch, the height was a hundred and twenty — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "This being a kind of turret to the building. How this may be reconciled with ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Kings 6:3",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", see the notes there. The breadth of it, here omitted, is there said to be ten cubits. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "The greater house he ceiled with fir-tree — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Namely, the ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "holy place, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "which was twice as large as the lesser house, or the holy of holies, which is called ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "the most holy house, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Chronicles 3:8",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The outward part of the former was of fir- tree, to bear the weather better; but the inside was lined with cedar, overlaid with gold, and figures, or sculptures, of palm-trees, chains, and other ornaments.",
        "children": []
      },
