        "text": "Cubits after the first measure",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". This possibly means the cubit of pre-Captivity times, but at all events the Israelites' own ancient cubit - perhaps a hand-breadth (",
        "children": []
